ols (pause/resume/stop) to renderer via IPC events in App.tsx\n- Default presets: 10 min, 25 min, 50 min; custom presets addable/removable in settings\n- Timer state is in-memory only (not persisted across app restarts)\n- Wrote 14 tests for timer store (formatTimeRemaining, DEFAULT_TIMER_PRESETS, store lifecycle)\n- All new and existing tests pass, zero typecheck errors"
